{"tid":958312,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好似我咁，好多疑？","createTime":"2018-12-27T16:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T17:39:40.000Z","uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efcceb17b3848edd77d11b4bedc21fcf945dd9b0","tid":958312,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"話說我早排識左條女<br />\n<br />\n之後聖誕節約左出黎，普通食下飯咁<br />\n<br />\n呢d時間日日都whatsapp，我有時冇搵佢，佢都會主動搵我<br />\n<br />\n佢會既行為令我覺得好疑惑...<br />\n<br />\n列如<br />\n<br />\n前日聖誕，佢未覆我出唔出黎，我問佢係咪出黎嫁...<br />\n<br />\n佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你今晚係咪出黎啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：做咩啊？你好想我出黎咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點解？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想見你囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：😏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前出黎都冇咩野，有講有笑咁，冇乜身體接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後琴日同佢傾計...講講佢無啦啦話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我今日收早，你有咩做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我約左人啊（其實自己一個係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦哦，我都約左fd,我聽日都收早，諗住1月1請假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦哦<br />\n<br />\n之後隔左陣...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我1月1請唔到假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點解既？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早比人拎哂d假，太遲拎唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：1月1唔係應該年年都拎定先既咩🤣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁我平日冇諗過過咩節日，都係自己一個人，咪冇拎定假...<br />\n<br />\n果一刻我唔知點答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我硬係覺得今次遇到高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：送過佢返屋企，唔知幾歲同做d咩（問佢佢話唔講）"},{"pid":"dc06d105b5a7f53be1076ef03ad0a41c2acd3e31","tid":958312,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"我想表達我唔知幾時開始好多疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識咩女我都抱住佢想呃錢既應覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fed070453af74e603b40cdc8bde78a0721ee631","tid":958312,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc06d105b5a7f53be1076ef03ad0a41c2acd3e31","tid":958312,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"我想表達我唔知幾時開始好多疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識咩女我都抱住佢想呃錢既應覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"感覺"},{"pid":"8ad5171fe8a37e0d33673369f31d5aaf579dc236","tid":958312,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"哦哦"},{"pid":"b770bedca83f0674fbf6755b6f3596b94a932e81","tid":958312,"uid":38352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"On99 想約人咪約 死毒撚"},{"pid":"e3fa3cc80e7ccf85a13cb7c14f934705d4d06733","tid":958312,"uid":217774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"直接問佢囉<br />\n君子坦蕩蕩 小人長jj"},{"pid":"e5088e99a8b674bbda4e43cfc54875